{"tid":1960552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑龍江新增20宗境外輸入病例　全為中國籍來自俄羅斯","createTime":"2020-04-06T08:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T09:28:20.000Z","uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e927b00eaad195de7db8cc34277de0857ec9d6b","tid":1960552,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/457338/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%8D%E6%B1%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E20%E5%AE%97%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E5%85%A8%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F457338%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%25B1%259F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E20%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B1%258D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=0fcc2b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/457338/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%8D%E6%B1%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E20%E5%AE%97%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E5%85%A8%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）疫情持續，在黑龍江省，周日（5日）0至24時新增20宗境外輸入確診病例，均為中國籍，且都是從俄羅斯輸入；截至5日24時，累計報告境外輸入確診病例42宗。<br />\n<br />\n此外，5日0至24時，黑龍江省無新增確診病例，無新增疑似病例。新增境外輸入重症病例4宗，其中重型3宗，危重型1宗。追蹤到境外密切接觸者759人，已解除醫學觀察272人，尚有487人正在接受醫學觀察。省內現有無症狀感染者2宗，包括哈爾濱市五常市1宗、七台河市勃利縣1宗。當日發熱門診診療人數787人。<br />\n<br />\n在黑龍江省，周日（5日）0至24時新增20宗境外輸入確診病例，均為中國籍，且都是從俄羅斯輸入。圖為哈爾濱中央大街。（中新社）<br />\n在黑龍江省，周日（5日）0至24時新增20宗境外輸入確診病例，均為中國籍，且都是從俄羅斯輸入。圖為哈爾濱中央大街。（中新社）<br />\n<br />\n5日0至24時，黑龍江新增境外輸入無症狀感染者28宗，均為中國籍，從俄羅斯輸入26宗、加拿大1宗、菲律賓1宗。截至4月5日24時，現有境外輸入無症狀感染者60宗。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯傳媒報道，當地上周六（4日）新增658宗確診病例，累計確診增至5300多宗，有45人染疫身亡。當局從當地時間3月30日零時起，已關閉所有跨越俄羅斯邊境的汽車、鐵路、行人、水上檢查站的交通，強調這是臨時措施，但未有重開時間表。"},{"pid":"c16283c1725b2cdd84f7236fa9bbbc9a4b29c83f","tid":1960552,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dc0b63d3cf46e2be6769cc5e2517f40dbd6338","tid":1960552,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49445b78f041396b5a5c64892a8ead00d53d2aca","tid":1960552,"uid":168400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"329096182e186f49da8319a6bf03a5af5b587418","tid":1960552,"uid":245441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"夠膽拉普京落水<br />\n呢招高。"},{"pid":"78a56aea2a125a076018d3f4778630e3fab60e6f","tid":1960552,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"中俄唔係封晒關? 點解有輸入?"},{"pid":"257380be4b2cb290204a8345a5ac1e4c686d8156","tid":1960552,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329096182e186f49da8319a6bf03a5af5b587418","tid":1960552,"uid":245441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"夠膽拉普京落水<br />\n呢招高。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"得罪全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}